I'm done.

41
00:06:40,750 --> 00:06:42,110
Then I am going up.

42
00:06:42,110 --> 00:06:44,660
Okay. Rest early.

43
00:06:45,630 --> 00:06:47,250
Goodnight.

44
00:06:47,250 --> 00:06:48,680
Goodnight.

45
