Leave him here so he can accompany me home, okay?

47
00:06:59,180 --> 00:07:01,960
I'll leave him with you. Get a good night's rest.

48
00:07:41,810 --> 00:07:44,390
Is he going to propose or not?

49
00:08:19,940 --> 00:08:22,050
Team Leader Xia,

50
00:08:22,050 --> 00:08:25,000
did you sign the document I gave you this morning?

51
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:26,360
Which one?

52
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:29,320
The one at the bottom. There.

53
00:08:37,090 --> 00:08:38,490
Okay, I looked over it.

54
00:08:38,490 --> 00:08:40,790
Thank you. You worked hard.

55
