72
00:10:00,390 --> 00:10:02,450
- I propose?
- Yes.

73
00:10:07,250 --> 00:10:08,870
Is that okay?

74
00:10:08,870 --> 00:10:11,980
Instead of you sitting here worrying about it, you could directly ask him.

75
00:10:11,980 --> 00:10:15,200
What Xiaoyan said is correct. I agree.

76
00:10:18,430 --> 00:10:20,370
I will propose to him.

77
00:10:20,370 --> 00:10:21,800
Cheers!

78
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:27,600
My phone!

79
00:10:30,420 --> 00:10:32,110
Where is it?

80
00:10:32,110 --> 00:10:33,780
There.

81
00:10:45,100 --> 00:10:47,300
[89]

82
00:10:50,790 --> 00:10:54,380
- Qianqian
- Come to my mom's barbecue stall.

83
00:10:54,380 --> 00:10:56,380
I have something important to tell you.

84
00:10:56,380 --> 00:10:58,070
What's wrong?

85
