What's wrong? Are you okay?

86
00:11:38,340 --> 00:11:40,330
You drank?

87
00:11:42,990 --> 00:11:45,350
Are you in a bad mood?

88
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:48,280
Who bullied you?

89
00:11:51,510 --> 00:11:54,290
Tell me. I will find them.

90
00:11:54,290 --> 00:11:56,380
You!

91
00:11:56,380 --> 00:11:59,810
- Me?
- Sheng Zhening,

92
00:11:59,810 --> 00:12:02,170
are you going to marry me?

93
00:12:06,920 --> 00:12:09,680
The ring was clearly placed on my hand before.

94
00:12:11,060 --> 00:12:13,230
Why did you take it off?

95
00:12:14,150 --> 00:12:17,650
And at the amusement park, weren't you going to propose?

96
00:12:17,650 --> 00:12:20,920
What happened? You didn't say a single thing.

97
00:12:20,920 --> 00:12:24,790
Then there was that cake which was not good at all.

98
00:12:24,790 --> 00:12:27,190
I thought the ring was hidden in there,

99
00:12:27,190 --> 00:12:29,230
so I ate the entire thing.

100
00:12:31,640 --> 00:12:34,950
What are you laughing at? I am being serious.

101
00:12:34,950 --> 00:12:38,400
It's because I wanted to give you something special.

102
00:12:38,400 --> 00:12:42,390
A grand and romantic proposal.

103
00:12:43,430 --> 00:12:47,490
That day at the amusement park and later that night at the restaurant,

104
00:12:47,490 --> 00:12:49,230
I had everything prepared

105
00:12:49,230 --> 00:12:52,820
but there were some small accidents.

106
00:12:57,160 --> 00:13:01,840
I don't need anything special or romantic.

107
00:13:02,480 --> 00:13:06,510
You are my romantic. You are the most special and unique.

108
00:13:08,120 --> 00:13:09,830
And?

109
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:12,910
Now...

110
00:13:13,470 --> 00:13:15,090
What?

111
00:13:19,880 --> 00:13:22,710
I'm a girl and I have already said this much.

112
00:13:22,710 --> 00:13:25,160
At this time shouldn't you say something?

113
00:13:25,160 --> 00:13:27,380
Propose!

114
00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:31,130
I-I rushed over here. I-I...

115
00:13:31,130 --> 00:13:33,580
don't have anything.

116
00:13:33,580 --> 00:13:35,230
Then,

117
00:13:39,290 --> 00:13:41,110
what do we do?

118
00:13:41,110 --> 00:13:43,740
- I don't eat that
- Propose!

119
00:13:43,740 --> 00:13:45,830
- What are you doing?
- Propose!

120
00:13:45,830 --> 00:13:47,670
This...

121
00:13:49,260 --> 00:13:51,000
What does this mean?

122
00:13:51,970 --> 00:13:54,230
Select one based on my measurements.

123
00:14:14,950 --> 00:14:17,090
Do it right here.

124
00:14:17,090 --> 00:14:19,020
This isn't good, right?

125
00:14:47,490 --> 00:14:53,050
Honestly, these past two days I have thought a lot.

126
00:14:53,880 --> 00:14:56,350
I finally understand,

127
00:14:57,630 --> 00:15:01,260
a woman accepting a man's proposal

128
00:15:01,260 --> 00:15:05,340
should not be an impulsive decision.

129
00:15:05,340 --> 00:15:07,950
A man's proposal should not

130
00:15:07,950 --> 00:15:11,230
be accepted because it automatically moves the woman.

131
00:15:11,830 --> 00:15:16,270
If you want the woman to give you her heart,

132
00:15:16,270 --> 00:15:18,670
for her to become your wife,

133
00:15:18,670 --> 00:15:21,860
starting from when they first meet,

134
00:15:21,860 --> 00:15:24,640
you start to work on it.

135
00:15:25,160 --> 00:15:29,080
So, in this world, there is no

136
00:15:29,080 --> 00:15:33,070
perfect proposal. Love...

137
00:15:33,070 --> 00:15:35,270
is two people's

138
00:15:35,270 --> 00:15:38,680
every moment, every second.

139
00:15:39,520 --> 00:15:44,150
It is understanding. It is tolerating.

140
00:15:45,890 --> 00:15:48,360
It is the beautiful scenery of the journey.

141
00:15:59,670 --> 00:16:03,140
Saying this much, I realized

142
00:16:03,140 --> 00:16:04,760
what I said is pretty weak.

143
00:16:04,760 --> 00:16:09,600
Only my actions of love are the truest.

144
00:16:12,890 --> 00:16:18,330
Are you willing to witness my sincerity?

145
00:16:26,360 --> 00:16:30,830
Marry him! Marry him!

146
00:16:30,830 --> 00:16:35,200
♫ You love me in this way ♫

147
00:16:35,200 --> 00:16:40,770
♫ Teach me to be honest to this world and myself ♫

148
00:16:40,770 --> 00:16:45,160
♫  Having each simple day in our hands  ♫

149
00:16:45,160 --> 00:16:49,430
♫  is already something extraordinary  ♫

150
00:16:50,660 --> 00:16:55,100
♫ If not for your insistence ♫

151
00:16:55,100 --> 00:16:59,370
♫ I wouldn't have known what love is  ♫

152
00:16:59,370 --> 00:17:04,900
♫  No matter how old we get, this time  ♫

153
00:17:04,900 --> 00:17:09,080
♫  We will slowly learn to walk with love  ♫

154
00:17:09,080 --> 00:17:11,340
I do.

155
00:17:11,340 --> 00:17:17,460
♫  Love needs to be warmed up slowly, walking slowly  ♫

156
00:17:17,460 --> 00:17:22,560
♫  Warm up slowly, from ordinary to impressive  ♫

157
00:17:22,560 --> 00:17:27,210
♫  Slowly, we become more similar  ♫

158
00:17:27,210 --> 00:17:31,170
♫  Our hearts are transparent  ♫

159
00:17:31,170 --> 00:17:37,200
♫  Love needs to be warmed up slowly,
as we understand each other  ♫

160
00:17:37,200 --> 00:17:42,220
♫  Slowly, I've found my angel  ♫

161
00:17:42,220 --> 00:17:46,960
♫  Even if the shiny were wrinkled  ♫

162
00:17:46,960 --> 00:17:54,930
♫  It is still happiness accumulated in life  ♫

163
00:18:11,340 --> 00:18:13,800
Saying this much, I realized

164
00:18:13,800 --> 00:18:14,970
what I said is pretty weak.

165
00:18:14,970 --> 00:18:19,740
Only my actions of love are the truest.

166
00:18:20,560 --> 00:18:25,960
Are you willing to witness my sincerity?

167
00:18:53,420 --> 00:18:55,870
Are you not going on a business trip today?

168
00:18:55,870 --> 00:18:58,800
You're awake? Get ready for breakfast.

169
00:19:00,690 --> 00:19:02,900
I had Director Sun go instead.

170
00:19:02,900 --> 00:19:06,110
I have more important things to do today.

171
00:19:06,110 --> 00:19:08,230
What important things?

172
00:19:09,370 --> 00:19:13,400
After eating breakfast, we should go to Liping Barbecue.

173
00:19:13,400 --> 00:19:17,870
I've already proposed, we should let your mom know about it.

174
00:19:38,550 --> 00:19:41,870
How about we go back to the hotel?

175
00:19:41,870 --> 00:19:43,620
What's wrong?

176
00:19:43,620 --> 00:19:47,950
My suit today doesn't feel formal enough.

177
00:19:48,560 --> 00:19:51,470
What side of you hasn't my mom seen?

178
00:19:51,470 --> 00:19:54,240
She will like whatever you wear.

179
00:19:54,240 --> 00:19:56,410
Don't be so scrupulous.

180
00:20:07,790 --> 00:20:11,460
Xiaoyan, with Sister Qian's engagement,

181
00:20:11,460 --> 00:20:13,900
what present do you plan to give her?

182
00:20:15,040 --> 00:20:17,950
I don't know. What are you gifting her?

183
00:20:18,650 --> 00:20:22,470
- I already bought it
- What are you giving her?

184
00:20:22,470 --> 00:20:25,080
I can't tell you.

185
00:20:27,460 --> 00:20:30,340
I suck at giving gifts.

186
00:20:30,340 --> 00:20:32,400
What do I do?

187
00:20:32,400 --> 00:20:34,830
I think they don't need anything,

188
00:20:34,830 --> 00:20:37,710
so gifts represent your regard.

189
00:20:37,710 --> 00:20:42,040
I think you should gift those things that they will use sooner or later.

190
00:20:42,040 --> 00:20:44,400
You need to think about it in the long run.

191
00:20:45,350 --> 00:20:48,300
Something they can use sooner or later?

192
00:20:50,340 --> 00:20:52,630
What are you thinking about?

193
00:20:52,630 --> 00:20:55,420
I think I should buy something. I can't just show up

194
00:20:55,420 --> 00:20:57,320
empty handed.

195
00:20:57,320 --> 00:21:02,180
There's no need. Telling my mom will make her happier than anything else could.

196
00:21:02,180 --> 00:21:04,130
Wait. Wait.

197
00:21:04,130 --> 00:21:07,940
Let me think about how to tell Auntie.

198
00:21:07,940 --> 00:21:11,900
Let's go. You don't need to think, you will know soon.

199
00:21:11,900 --> 00:21:13,940
Hurry up.

200
00:21:13,940 --> 00:21:17,160
Let's go. Why are you so heavy?

201
00:21:18,250 --> 00:21:20,180
Go in.

202
00:21:24,130 --> 00:21:26,970
This time Chef Hu made a good purchase. It smells good.

203
00:21:26,970 --> 00:21:28,880
Tell her.

204
00:21:31,930 --> 00:21:34,840
- What's wrong? Why are you so serious?
- He has something to say.

205
00:21:34,840 --> 00:21:36,760
Say it.

206
00:21:37,980 --> 00:21:42,440
Auntie, I proposed to her.

207
00:21:44,190 --> 00:21:47,320
- Really?
- Mom.

208
00:21:50,780 --> 00:21:54,470
I know Qianqian is your most important person

209
00:21:54,470 --> 00:21:57,010
so I will definitely love her,

210
00:21:57,010 --> 00:21:59,540
respect her, protect her. I hope you—

211
00:21:59,540 --> 00:22:02,430
I agree. I agree.

212
00:22:02,430 --> 00:22:04,930
Then, when will you have the wedding?

213
00:22:04,930 --> 00:22:08,330
See? My mom didn't even have to think about it.

214
00:22:08,330 --> 00:22:13,090
Think about it? It is so hard to find a son-in-law as good as Xiao Sheng. Why would I think about it?

215
00:22:13,090 --> 00:22:15,430
B-But Auntie, don't you

216
00:22:15,430 --> 00:22:18,880
want to hear about our plans for the future

217
00:22:18,880 --> 00:22:21,210
- and life—
- I don't want to hear about it.

218
00:22:21,210 --> 00:22:24,050
No, that's not what I mean.

219
00:22:24,050 --> 00:22:27,250
You, young people, have your own plans.

220
00:22:27,250 --> 00:22:31,640
You have your own pace for life. I don't want to interfere too much.

221
00:22:31,640 --> 00:22:35,980
Besides, I won't even understand if you tried to explain your jobs to me.

222
00:22:38,880 --> 00:22:42,150
But, about getting married,

223
00:22:42,150 --> 00:22:45,460
there are a few things I want to tell you.

224
00:22:45,460 --> 00:22:48,390
Don't mind me being wordy.

225
00:22:48,390 --> 00:22:52,500
Marriage life is not as romantic as you think,

226
00:22:52,500 --> 00:22:54,430
it is not like how it is on TV.

227
00:22:54,430 --> 00:22:57,470
Just shopping, cooking,

228
00:22:57,470 --> 00:23:00,230
watching TV will not allow you to maintain the relationship.

229
00:23:00,230 --> 00:23:04,160
Marriage requires managing and protecting from the both of you.

230
00:23:04,160 --> 00:23:08,530
Of course, it is not a simple thing.

231
00:23:08,530 --> 00:23:11,090
Once you guys have lived together for a long time,

232
00:23:11,090 --> 00:23:14,190
there will be some clashes, some conflicts.

233
00:23:14,190 --> 00:23:17,120
During these times do not be dissatisfied.

234
00:23:17,120 --> 00:23:21,330
Be tolerant and understanding. Learn to stand in the other's shoes and see things from their point of view.

235
00:23:21,330 --> 00:23:24,290
Think about each other's benefits and forgive them.

236
00:23:24,290 --> 00:23:25,980
The most important thing is that

237
00:23:25,980 --> 00:23:29,820
you need to trust one another.

238
00:23:29,820 --> 00:23:35,430
That way your marriage can last a long time.

239
00:23:37,660 --> 00:23:39,670
Aunt, I understand.

240
00:23:41,120 --> 00:23:43,870
Since you're so easygoing today,

241
00:23:45,910 --> 00:23:47,480
let's not mention children...

242
00:23:47,480 --> 00:23:49,660
You guys should have children soon.

243
00:23:49,660 --> 00:23:52,970
It's a very important thing! How old are you?

244
00:23:52,970 --> 00:23:58,000
Pre-pregnancy and prenatal care is very complicated. There are a long of things to prepare.

245
00:23:58,000 --> 00:23:59,820
Old Hu! Old Hu!

246
00:23:59,820 --> 00:24:01,470
No, stop yelling.

247
00:24:01,470 --> 00:24:03,910
I'm asking him to prepare some chicken soup.

248
00:24:03,910 --> 00:24:08,730
We have to make chicken soup, and you have to eat it every day.

249
00:24:08,730 --> 00:24:11,610
I won't count on him. I'll buy a chicken and make chicken soup for you now.

250
00:24:11,610 --> 00:24:13,170
Bye!

251
00:24:16,720 --> 00:24:18,580
That's how she is.

252
00:24:19,320 --> 00:24:20,920
Excuse me.

253
00:24:22,040 --> 00:24:24,320
Why are you here?

254
00:24:24,320 --> 00:24:26,260
What a coincidence.

255
00:24:26,260 --> 00:24:29,440
- You're buying babies clothes, too?
- Yeah.

256
00:24:29,440 --> 00:24:31,570
Is there anyone in your family expecting a baby?

257
00:24:31,570 --> 00:24:33,580
No.

258
00:24:33,580 --> 00:24:35,480
Then why...?

259
00:24:37,540 --> 00:24:39,460
You can't be buying this for...

260
00:24:39,460 --> 00:24:42,970
Yeah. An engagement gift for Miss Xia and GM Sheng.

261
00:24:42,970 --> 00:24:44,540
You can't do that.

262
00:24:44,540 --> 00:24:46,110
Why not?

263
00:24:46,110 --> 00:24:49,190
Because I'm buying this as a gift. We can't buy the same thing.

264
00:24:49,190 --> 00:24:52,380
Then you should get something else! I was here first.

265
00:24:52,380 --> 00:24:54,430
I decided yesterday!

266
00:24:54,430 --> 00:24:56,950
I decided yesterday evening.

267
00:24:59,860 --> 00:25:02,160
Hi, please wrap this for me.

268
00:25:02,790 --> 00:25:04,230
Are you paying together?

269
00:25:04,230 --> 00:25:05,640
- Separately.
- Separately.

270
00:25:05,640 --> 00:25:07,290
Okay.

271
00:25:09,920 --> 00:25:13,870
The clothes you bought won't be useful. GM Sheng likes girls.

272
00:25:13,870 --> 00:25:17,080
Who knows if they'll have a girl or a boy?

273
00:25:19,450 --> 00:25:21,590
- Thank you.
- Thank you.

274
00:25:39,440 --> 00:25:43,750
I can tell from your tone over the phone. It must be good news.

275
00:25:43,750 --> 00:25:46,050
Tell me how he proposed to you. Tell me now!

276
00:25:46,050 --> 00:25:50,600
Please! Tell me about it! Now!

277
00:25:50,600 --> 00:25:53,350
- You already know.
- Was it really romantic?

278
00:25:53,350 --> 00:25:57,780
Well, the scene of the proposal wasn't that romantic.

279
00:25:57,780 --> 00:26:01,410
What? Tell me about it. What was it like?

280
00:26:03,310 --> 00:26:06,270
I got very desperate. So I proposed to him.

281
00:26:06,270 --> 00:26:08,170
- You proposed to him?
- Yeah.

282
00:26:08,170 --> 00:26:10,360
No way!

283
00:26:12,190 --> 00:26:14,620
While I was drunk,

284
00:26:14,620 --> 00:26:19,360
I urged him to use the squid ring from my mom's barbecue house

285
00:26:19,360 --> 00:26:21,550
and put it on my finger.

286
00:26:22,550 --> 00:26:25,390
- Squid ring! That's awesome!
- And then,

287
00:26:25,390 --> 00:26:29,220
all of the guests in the barbecue house witnessed our proposal.

288
00:26:29,220 --> 00:26:30,430
- Isn't it romantic?
- It is.

289
00:26:30,430 --> 00:26:31,990
- Isn't it awesome?
- Yeah!

290
00:26:31,990 --> 00:26:34,630
Too bad I wasn't there.

291
00:26:36,260 --> 00:26:37,810
You were the only one missing.

292
00:26:37,810 --> 00:26:39,690
I'm so happy for you.

293
00:26:39,690 --> 00:26:43,220
What about you? Are you dating someone?

294
00:26:46,340 --> 00:26:48,620
Why are you sighing?

295
00:26:48,620 --> 00:26:52,690
I'm not sighing. I mean,

296
00:26:52,690 --> 00:26:56,080
Qin Hebo and I are dating, too.

297
00:26:57,790 --> 00:27:00,200
- That's what I guessed.
- How did you guess?

298
00:27:00,200 --> 00:27:02,410
How could I not guess right?

299
00:27:02,410 --> 00:27:06,480
You've been spending day and night together, and he's always on your mind.

300
00:27:06,480 --> 00:27:09,510
It would happen sooner or later. I think this is great.

301
00:27:10,700 --> 00:27:13,610
Do you think that I'm...

302
00:27:13,610 --> 00:27:17,620
Shuangshuang, you have my blessings. I'm happy for you.

303
00:27:18,890 --> 00:27:23,560
I mean it. And it's up to you to decide who you like or love.

304
00:27:23,560 --> 00:27:27,560
It has nothing to do with anyone else. I hope you can be happy.

305
00:27:27,560 --> 00:27:29,730
Thank you, Qianqian.

306
00:27:30,880 --> 00:27:33,160
That's great.

307
00:27:33,160 --> 00:27:36,550
- It looks stunning!
- You need a squid ring, too.

308
00:27:36,550 --> 00:27:38,660
Tell my mom when you need it.

309
00:27:38,660 --> 00:27:41,120
- Come to our barbecue house!
- Okay!

310
00:27:51,110 --> 00:27:54,090
- Mengmeng.
- Brother, you're here.

311
00:27:54,090 --> 00:27:56,490
Take a seat. I'll be right there.

312
00:27:56,490 --> 00:27:58,150
Okay.

313
00:28:13,280 --> 00:28:15,590
Brother, try this.

314
00:28:19,650 --> 00:28:21,340
Is it delicious?

315
00:28:21,340 --> 00:28:23,160
It tastes great.

316
00:28:27,090 --> 00:28:31,720
Brother, I've been thinking a lot recently.

317
00:28:31,720 --> 00:28:36,720
I was too immature before. I'm sorry.

318
00:28:38,990 --> 00:28:40,490
Mengmeng.

319
00:28:41,890 --> 00:28:47,890
This Sunday, Xia Qian and I will have a simple engagement party.

320
00:28:57,470 --> 00:28:59,340
I don't think I should go.

321
00:28:59,340 --> 00:29:02,980
I don't want to make it awkward for everyone.

322
00:29:10,460 --> 00:29:11,990
Okay.

323
00:29:15,630 --> 00:29:19,110
Qianqian, I'm sorry that I can't attend your engagement party

324
00:29:19,110 --> 00:29:22,060
because of work.

325
00:29:22,060 --> 00:29:26,550
I'm truly happy to see you starting a new life with the one you love.

326
00:29:26,550 --> 00:29:31,920
May happiness and peace be with you, and I hope all your wishes can come true.

327
00:29:32,560 --> 00:29:35,430
Your friend forever, Shuangshuang.

328
00:29:44,760 --> 00:29:46,630
I'm back.

329
00:29:47,460 --> 00:29:50,100
Wash your hands. I'll get the soup.

330
00:29:57,450 --> 00:29:59,490
The soup is here.

331
00:30:01,460 --> 00:30:03,060
Okay, time for dinner.

332
00:30:03,060 --> 00:30:06,290
I saw the gift you prepared.

333
00:30:08,830 --> 00:30:12,090
That's the engagement gift for Qianqian and Sheng Zhening.

334
00:30:12,090 --> 00:30:16,770
Their engagement party will be held at Evergreen Hotel on Sunday evening.

335
00:30:16,770 --> 00:30:19,160
I'll drive you there.

336
00:30:19,160 --> 00:30:22,660
I have to live stream that evening. I don't think I'm going.

337
00:30:22,660 --> 00:30:25,660
You can reschedule it for the afternoon. It's fine.

338
00:30:25,660 --> 00:30:29,300
It's okay. Qianqian won't mind.

339
00:30:29,300 --> 00:30:31,500
As long as my wishes are there.

340
00:30:46,160 --> 00:30:50,120
I know it's all because of me, right?

341
00:30:54,320 --> 00:30:56,020
I'm sorry.

342
00:30:57,040 --> 00:31:00,400
I know that Xia Qian is a very important friend to you.

343
00:31:02,660 --> 00:31:05,300
Now I've put you in a difficult spot.

344
00:31:05,300 --> 00:31:07,060
No, it's okay.

345
00:31:09,800 --> 00:31:12,340
Give me some more time.

346
00:31:12,340 --> 00:31:17,590
I'll solve all the problems between Zhening and me. Okay?

347
00:31:18,900 --> 00:31:21,460
Thank you for saying this to me.

348
00:31:21,460 --> 00:31:23,820
I'll always be there for you.

349
00:31:30,930 --> 00:31:32,900
Let's have dinner.

350
00:31:37,400 --> 00:31:39,890
- What are you doing?
- What's in the boxes?

351
00:31:39,890 --> 00:31:42,290
Don't touch it yet. Didn't I ask you two to come together?

352
00:31:42,290 --> 00:31:44,990
Why are you here alone? Where is he?

353
00:31:45,830 --> 00:31:49,070
He's in a meeting. He'll be here soon.

354
00:31:49,070 --> 00:31:51,030
Tell me. What's happening?

355
00:31:51,030 --> 00:31:54,690
What is it? Two mysterious boxes.

356
00:31:55,970 --> 00:31:59,060
These are the gifts I've prepared for you and Xiao Sheng.

357
00:31:59,060 --> 00:32:01,800
They are very valuable.

358
00:32:01,800 --> 00:32:04,290
Guess how much they are.

359
00:32:07,300 --> 00:32:09,130
They look festive.

360
00:32:09,130 --> 00:32:11,230
Let me give you a hint.

361
00:32:12,840 --> 00:32:14,860
2,000?

362
00:32:14,860 --> 00:32:18,130
You think your mom's that stingy? Make a better guess.

363
00:32:18,130 --> 00:32:20,430
You spent 20,000?

364
00:32:20,430 --> 00:32:22,560
Guess again.

365
00:32:24,830 --> 00:32:26,600
200,000?

366
00:32:27,580 --> 00:32:30,300
Are you crazy? 200,000?

367
00:32:30,300 --> 00:32:33,460
Mom, why did you spend 200,000 yuan on these?

368
00:32:33,460 --> 00:32:35,300
Did you get ripped off, Mom?

369
00:32:35,300 --> 00:32:38,430
Of course, I didn't get ripped off. They're worth that much.

370
00:32:38,430 --> 00:32:40,700
Why did you spend so much money?

371
00:32:40,700 --> 00:32:42,630
And where did you get so much money?

372
00:32:42,630 --> 00:32:44,800
I... I've saved some money.

373
00:32:44,800 --> 00:32:49,470
And I borrowed the rest from Uncle Hu.

374
00:32:49,470 --> 00:32:53,000
But he said that there's no rush to pay him back.

375
00:32:55,360 --> 00:32:57,700
You really don't have to do this.

376
00:32:57,700 --> 00:33:01,000
As long as we have your wishes. Zhening would understand.

377
00:33:01,000 --> 00:33:03,540
You don't have to buy such expensive gifts.

378
00:33:03,540 --> 00:33:07,030
I know that he doesn't care about this sort of stuff.

379
00:33:07,030 --> 00:33:09,020
But I can see

380
00:33:09,020 --> 00:33:11,240
how well he's been treating you.

381
00:33:11,240 --> 00:33:13,470
Our family isn't rich.

382
00:33:13,470 --> 00:33:19,900
But as your parent, shouldn't I prepare a decent gift for him?

383
00:33:21,320 --> 00:33:23,090
Thank you, Mom.

384
00:33:25,290 --> 00:33:28,790
Xia Qian, you know, Mom was hoping every day

385
00:33:28,790 --> 00:33:32,050
that you could get married soon.

386
00:33:32,720 --> 00:33:35,660
But now you're getting married for real,

387
00:33:36,470 --> 00:33:40,530
I feel reluctant to let you go.

388
00:33:46,380 --> 00:33:49,790
- Why are you laughing?
- I mean,

389
00:33:49,790 --> 00:33:52,650
I haven't seen you like this for many years, Mom.

390
00:33:52,650 --> 00:33:54,820
There, there.

391
00:33:54,820 --> 00:33:58,770
Stop crying. How about this?

392
00:33:58,770 --> 00:34:02,320
Mom, I can't just watch you cry. I'll take off the ring. I won't get married.

393
00:34:02,320 --> 00:34:05,520
Stop messing around. How's that possible?

394
00:34:08,980 --> 00:34:10,960
Aunt.

395
00:34:10,960 --> 00:34:13,860
- Xiao Sheng!
- Were you looking for me?

396
00:34:13,860 --> 00:34:17,120
You're here. Take a seat.

397
00:34:19,650 --> 00:34:26,730
You are about to be engaged to Xia Qian. I have prepared a present to give you both.

398
00:34:26,730 --> 00:34:32,450
See if you like it. This is a pair of Dragon Phoenix necklaces.
(TN: from an idiom that means the dragon and phoenix are symbols of good fortune)

399
00:34:32,450 --> 00:34:37,710
I hope in the future the two of you will live peacefully, beautifully, and in prosperity.

400
00:34:37,710 --> 00:34:41,070
See if you like it.

401
00:34:47,010 --> 00:34:49,180
How is it?

402
00:34:49,180 --> 00:34:53,540
I like it. This is very unique.

403
00:34:53,540 --> 00:34:56,210
- You should open it too.
- I won't

404
00:34:56,210 --> 00:34:58,920
- Quickly!
- I'll see, I'll see.

405
00:35:01,240 --> 00:35:03,550
Yours is a Phoenix.

406
00:35:03,550 --> 00:35:06,380
On your engagement day, both of you wear these.

407
00:35:06,380 --> 00:35:11,500
No, No, No, not wearing these. These do not fit our engagement outfits.

408
00:35:11,500 --> 00:35:16,690
What's wrong with wearing these? If not, you can still wear them inside!

409
00:35:16,690 --> 00:35:21,780
It's okay. I'll wear it, it looks nice. It's good.

410
00:35:21,780 --> 00:35:25,010
Look at him, wear it!

411
00:35:25,010 --> 00:35:27,170
I'll wear it.

412
00:35:28,970 --> 00:35:31,190
Okay, on your engagement day, wear it around your neck.

413
00:35:31,190 --> 00:35:32,390
I'll wear it inside.

414
00:35:32,390 --> 00:35:35,550
- Dragon Phoenix brings good luck.
- I know.

415
00:35:35,550 --> 00:35:38,070
Not practical.

416
00:35:38,740 --> 00:35:40,880
Are you sick?

417
00:35:44,300 --> 00:35:47,930
Come, let me take it off. Don't wear it, it's old-fashioned.

418
00:35:47,930 --> 00:35:51,030
Aunt's token of regard, I need to wear it.

419
00:35:51,030 --> 00:35:53,250
Okay, stuff it inside.

420
00:35:54,050 --> 00:35:57,810
On top of my shirt. Do you have time tomorrow?

421
00:35:57,810 --> 00:36:00,550
Tomorrow? Yes, I have time.

422
00:36:00,550 --> 00:36:03,330
Okay. I'll take you somewhere.

423
00:36:06,030 --> 00:36:07,750
Let's go.

424
00:36:18,090 --> 00:36:19,520
Here.

425
00:36:34,010 --> 00:36:36,100
[Father: Sheng Shaoxuan
Mother: Ning Shuying]

426
00:36:36,100 --> 00:36:40,150
Dad. Mom. I've come here to see you.

427
00:36:41,570 --> 00:36:47,950
Telling you both, I'm engaged. This is my fiancé, her name is Xia Qian.

428
00:36:51,850 --> 00:36:57,890
Hi, Uncle and Auntie. Please rest assured, I'll take good care of Zhening.

429
00:37:00,110 --> 00:37:04,500
There are some things that I've been hiding in my heart.

430
00:37:04,500 --> 00:37:07,220
Before joining Evergreen Hotel,

431
00:37:08,040 --> 00:37:13,600
I've always had a dream, I wanted to be a violinist.

432
00:37:14,760 --> 00:37:16,790
Violinist?

433
00:37:23,880 --> 00:37:25,950
- Please enjoy.
- Thank you.

434
00:37:35,270 --> 00:37:37,340
[Ning Meng: Dad, I'm stuck in traffic and will be there later. You and Brother can eat first.]

435
00:38:21,580 --> 00:38:27,920
Dad! Dad! Brother wanted to give you a surprise and perform especially for you. Dad!

436
00:38:36,180 --> 00:38:37,780
You come down!

437
00:38:49,210 --> 00:38:53,800
Why didn't you attend this afternoon's board meeting?

438
00:38:56,690 --> 00:38:59,540
I didn't agree that I would go at all.

439
00:38:59,540 --> 00:39:02,110
You knew the purpose of me organizing the meeting.

440
00:39:02,110 --> 00:39:05,650
To introduce the shareholders to you. But look at you!

441
00:39:05,650 --> 00:39:10,130
You didn't say anything, didn't even come. Do you know that

442
00:39:10,130 --> 00:39:16,520
it would result in the partners losing trust in you. This is a big corporate taboo, do you know?

443
00:39:21,420 --> 00:39:24,370
What do you want to say? You can tell me.

444
00:39:24,370 --> 00:39:28,510
I absolutely don't care about corporate rules

445
00:39:28,510 --> 00:39:33,260
and what management tips are. I asked you to meet me here today,

446
00:39:33,940 --> 00:39:39,170
was to tell you I had my own ideas, my own dreams.

447
00:39:39,170 --> 00:39:43,700
I absolutely do not want to enter Evergreen's board. These years,

448
00:39:43,700 --> 00:39:48,100
it's always been your arrangements, your ideas. Did you even ask for my opinions?

449
00:39:49,320 --> 00:39:54,380
Since I was young, I've listened to you. Now I want to play the violin.

450
00:39:54,380 --> 00:39:57,670
This one time, I need you to acknowledge me. Is it so hard?

451
00:39:57,670 --> 00:40:00,050
Brother don't say too much.

452
00:40:00,050 --> 00:40:04,830
Dad, you just let brother do what he likes.

453
00:40:08,850 --> 00:40:10,700
Are you done talking?

454
00:40:12,410 --> 00:40:16,000
There will be a business forum the day after tomorrow. You have to attend.

455
00:40:16,000 --> 00:40:19,650
I'll ask Xiao Qin to send you the time and location.

456
00:40:19,650 --> 00:40:22,570
I have a competition. I can't attend.

457
00:40:27,090 --> 00:40:28,990
Young man.

458
00:40:30,090 --> 00:40:35,170
I trained you for so many years, not for you to play the violin here.

459
00:40:35,170 --> 00:40:39,210
If you keep doing this, I'll cut ties with you.

460
00:40:54,680 --> 00:40:58,270
My father had an accident on his way home.

461
00:40:58,270 --> 00:41:01,810
If I had known that it was the last time to see him,

462
00:41:03,600 --> 00:41:07,910
I wouldn't have argued with him. Instead, I would have had a good chat with him.

463
00:41:07,910 --> 00:41:12,230
Later, I took over Evergreen. Every day,

464
00:41:12,730 --> 00:41:17,870
I had to put on a face of fake confidence in front of all the shareholders.

465
00:41:17,870 --> 00:41:20,750
Only when when it was late at night,

466
00:41:21,730 --> 00:41:24,650
I knew how much I doubted myself.

467
00:41:25,570 --> 00:41:30,030
Only then did I realize that judging from my father's perspective,

468
00:41:30,650 --> 00:41:35,860
having me join Evergreen was the best acknowledgment I could get.

469
00:41:36,630 --> 00:41:39,230
After I took over Evergreen, I realized

470
00:41:39,230 --> 00:41:45,410
how hard it was to manage such a big company without anyone you can trust by your side.

471
00:41:48,170 --> 00:41:52,400
This understanding came too late.

472
00:41:52,400 --> 00:41:54,680
My father can't ever hear it again.

473
00:41:56,480 --> 00:42:00,050
I'm sure your father will understand.

474
00:42:00,950 --> 00:42:05,900
And I'm sure he doesn't want you to feel sad about it now.

475
00:42:12,230 --> 00:42:15,260
I'll wait for you at the entrance.

476
00:42:34,990 --> 00:42:36,670
Sunflowers?

477
00:42:38,720 --> 00:42:41,810
When I was working as the assistant to Old GM Sheng,

478
00:42:41,810 --> 00:42:46,470
I'd put sunflowers in his office every day, as he requested.

479
00:42:46,470 --> 00:42:51,530
Back then, he always said that there are too many things to worry about during one's life,

480
00:42:51,530 --> 00:42:54,540
and that we have to find something to remind ourselves

481
00:42:54,540 --> 00:42:56,510
that we should try to be happy every day.

482
00:42:57,820 --> 00:43:02,260
After all these years, you still remember my father's likes and preferences.

483
00:43:02,840 --> 00:43:04,850
As I should.

484
00:43:08,950 --> 00:43:10,640
By the way,

485
00:43:10,640 --> 00:43:12,850
I heard that you're getting engaged.

486
00:43:14,810 --> 00:43:18,030
- Congratulations.
- Thank you.

487
00:43:37,680 --> 00:43:41,970
♫ You said don’t understand, then don’t understand ♫

